                                                                        <div class="fl-accordion-content fl-clearfix"><p style="text-align: left;"><strong><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-1333" src="https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/56-1-300x223.jpg" alt="Golf" width="300" height="223" srcset="https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/56-1-300x223.jpg 300w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/56-1-768x570.jpg 768w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/56-1-1024x761.jpg 1024w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/56-1.jpg 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px">Gladstan Golf Course</strong></p><p style="text-align: left;">Gladstan Golf Course is located in Payson just 15 minutes south of Provo, Utah and boasts beautiful rolling fairways, plentiful bunkers, water and amazing views.</p><p style="text-align: left;">Enjoying eating at the Gladstan Grill before or after golfing. The food is delicious and the view is wonderful if you sit on the deck and look over the valley!</p><p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://foreupsoftware.com/index.php/booking/index/18922#teetimes" target="_blank">Book a Tee time!</a></p></div>
