                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div class="fl-accordion-content fl-clearfix"><div id="attachment_1726" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1726" src="https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/81-2-300x200.jpg" alt="Community Alert System" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/81-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/81-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/81-2-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://paysonutah.org/storage/2016/05/81-2.jpg 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"><p class="wp-caption-text">Community Alert System</p></div><p>Get alerts about emergencies and other important community news by signing up for our Emergency Alert Program. This system enables us to provide you with critical information quickly in a variety of situations, such as severe weather, law enforcement activity, missing persons and evacuations of buildings or neighborhoods.</p><p><a href="https://member.everbridge.net/index/1332612387832225#/login">Sign up now</a></p></div>
